<%- include('partials/header.ejs') %> <%- include('partials/navigation.ejs') %>

<main>
  <h1>Services</h1>

  <section for="web-design">
    <header id="web-design">
      <h2 class="uppercase">Web Design</h2>
    </header>
    <p>
      With the latest technologies, who are recognized by the top companies like
      Facebook, Twitter, Tesla and more, we offer you unique websites with
      exceptional speed (tested by Google) and modern design specialized for
      your business. We build trust and easier communication between you and
      your clients, overcoming your competition in the digital world.
    </p>
    <button class="btn primary-btn" id="toggle-package-design">Packages</button>

    <div id="package-design" class="flex-wrap">
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Responsive Design</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Animations</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">SEO</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Unlimited Pages</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Contact Form</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Illustrations</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Content Writing</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">Images + Editing</p>
    </div>

    <p>
      If the price of your website is above 500&euro;, you get 3 months free
      hosting.
    </p>
    <p>
      If the price of your website is above 1.000&euro;, you get 6 months free
      hosting.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section for="web-hosting">
    <header id="web-hosting">
      <h2 class="uppercase">Web Hosting</h2>
    </header>
    <p>
      We recognized that hosting a website is unknown to our clients, which made
      us introduce a complete experience with developing and hosting websites.
      Strax Designs offers you maintaining your website and server, taking the
      responsibility as our obligation.
    </p>
    <button class="btn primary-btn" id="toggle-package-hosting">
      Packages
    </button>

    <div id="package-hosting" class="flex-wrap">
      <p class="details-item uppercase">6 months</p>
      <p class="details-item uppercase">12 months</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section for="work-process">
    <header id="work-process">
      <h2 class="uppercase">Work Process</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="carousel-container">
      <div id="carousel" class="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="carousel-item-flex">
            <img src="" alt="" />
            <h3>Meet Up</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Starting things off with a meeting about your business and what you
            do.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="carousel-item-flex">
            <img src="" alt="" />
            <h3>Analyze</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            We research your competition, so we can make sure you stand out from
            them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="carousel-item-flex">
            <img src="" alt="" />
            <h3>Design</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            We create a prototype of your website, and send it so you can
            review.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="carousel-item-flex">
            <img src="" alt="" />
            <h3>Code</h3>
          </div>
          <p>If you are happy with the design, we proceed to code it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="carousel-item-flex">
            <img src="" alt="" />
            <h3>Finish</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            After your website is ready, depending from your choice we either
            deliver it to you or host it for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-buttons">
        <button class="btn primary-btn" id="carousel-item-next"></button
        ><button class="btn primary-btn" id="carousel-item-prev"></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
